column17: Note: 1. Request selection is enabled only when current stage of the Project is set and PM Plan is in submitter stage. 2. Selected Request Type(s) will be available only when PM Plan is baselined. 3. Once PM Plan is baselined, please logout and login to see the changes.
column28: Note: Activity Code deselection may result in check-in failure.Please make sure that those activity codes are not being used for any tasks in the requests.
